{
  "chapter": 21,
  "chapter_summary": "萧十一郎与沈璧君被困在天公子的庄院中，被迫假扮夫妻。沈璧君恐惧绝望，萧十一郎温柔安慰并制定三步逃脱计划：养伤、破解魔法秘密、查明庄院中两个神秘老人的身份。雷雨趁萧十一郎不在时调戏沈璧君，被沈璧君以沈家金针吓退。萧十一郎为获取情报，主动接近庄院少女苏燕，从她口中得知两个神秘老人武功极高、连雷雨都惧怕三分。萧十一郎回来后沈璧君吃醋，他承诺不再去问少女们。第六天，萧十一郎在八角亭中与绿袍老人展开了一场无声的内力较量——以斟酒为名，三人纹丝不动对峙近五个时辰，展现了超凡的定力与内功。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你睡，我就在这里守护。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你看来很虚弱，现在我们绝不能倒下去。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我……我睡不着。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你还没有睡，怎么知道睡不着？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你怕？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你在怕我？……怕我也变得和那些人一样？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我的确是在怕，怕得很。这里每个人我都怕，每样东西我都怕，简直怕得要死，可是……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我并不怕你，我知道你永远不会变的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你既然相信我，就该听我的话。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "可是……可是……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "可是我们该怎么办呢？怎么办呢？难道我们真要在这里过一辈子，跟那些……那些……那些人过一辈子？",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "总有法子的，你放心，总有法子的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "可是你并没有把握。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我的确没把握。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "但我们还有希望。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "希望？什么希望？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "也许我能想出法子来破天公子的魔咒。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "那要等多久？十年？二十年？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "求求你，求求你让我做一件事。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你说。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "求求你让我去做那恶魔的祭典，我情愿去，莫说要我在这里呆十年二十年，就算叫我再呆一天，我都会发疯。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我虽然不是你的妻子，可是……为了你，我情愿死，只要你能好好的活着，无论叫我怎么样都没关系。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你……你答应了？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "要去，应该由我去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你——",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你有家、有亲人、有前途、有希望，应该活着的。但是我呢？只不过是个无足轻重的流浪汉，什么都没有，我死了，谁也不会关心。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "原来你还不明白我的心，一点也不明白，否则你怎会说死了也没有人关心，你若死了，我……我……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我什么都明白。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "那么你为什么要说？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我虽然那么说，可是我并没有真的准备去做那恶魔的祭礼！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我也绝不准你去！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "那么……那么你难道准备在这里过一辈子？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "跟你在一起，就算住在地狱里，我也不会怨，可是这里……这里却比地狱还邪恶，比地狱还可怕！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我们当然要想法子离开这里，但却绝不能用那种法子。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "因为我们若是那样做了，结果一定更悲惨。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你认为天公子不会遵守他的诺言？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我认为这只不过是个圈套。他非但要我们死，在我们死前，还要尽量作弄我们、折磨我们，令我们痛苦！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我认为他不但是个恶魔，还是个疯子！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我们若是为了要活着，不惜牺牲自己心爱的人，向他求饶，他非但不会放过我们，还会对我们嘲弄、讥笑。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "但你也并不能确定，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "但我已确定他是个疯子，何况，他说的这法子本就充满了矛盾，试想一个人若为了自己要活着，就不惜牺牲他的妻子，那么他岂非显然将自己的性命看得比他妻子重，他既然将自己性命看得最重，就该用自己的性命作祭礼才是，他既已用性命做祭礼，又何必再求别人放他？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "一个人若死了，还有什么魔法能将他拘禁得住？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我们既然已没有希望，不如现在就死吧！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我不知道你怎么想，但我却早已觉得，活着反而痛苦，只有'死'，才是最好的解脱！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "有时，死的确是种解脱，但却只不过是懦夫和弱者的解脱！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "现在还没有到死的时候，我们至少要先试试，究竟能不能逃出去？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "但那位庄主说的话也很有理，在别人眼中，我们已无异蝼蚁，只要用一块小石头，就能将我们压死。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "要逃，自然不容易，所以我必须先做好三件事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "哪三件？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "第一，我要等伤势好些。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "那位天公子显然不愿我死得太快，已替我治过伤，也不知他用的是什么魔法，还是医药，反正灵得很，我想再过几天，我的伤也许就会好了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "但愿如此。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "第二，我得先找出破解他的魔法和秘密。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你认为那秘密真在这庄院中？你认为这件事他没有说谎？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "每个人都有赌性，疯子尤其喜欢赌，所以他一定会故意留下个破绽，赌我们找不找得到。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "还有第三件事呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你看到亭子里的那两个人了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我总觉得这两个老头子很特别。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "特别？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "若是我猜得不错，这两人一定也是在江湖中绝迹已久的武林高人，而且比雷雨和龙飞骥还要可怕得多。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "所以，你想先查明他们两人究竟是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我只希望他们不是我想像中的那两个人，否则，就只他们这一关，我们也许都无法闯过。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "用过饭了么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_lei_yu",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "今天是老高掌勺，据说他本是京城里'鹿鸣香'的大师傅，手艺很不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_lei_yu",
      "text": "哦。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "这院子虽不太大，但若没有人陪着，也会迷路，姑娘若一不小心，闯到庄主的屋里去，那可不是好玩的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_lei_yu",
      "text": "谁是姑娘？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "不是姑娘，是夫人？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_lei_yu",
      "text": "哼。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "夫人可知道你的丈夫现在在什么地方吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_lei_yu",
      "text": "你知道？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我当然知道。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_lei_yu",
      "text": "却不知他在哪里，我正要找他。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "以我看，还是莫要找的好，找了反而烦恼。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_lei_yu",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你要我说真话？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_lei_yu",
      "text": "当然。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你知道，这里有很多很美丽的小姑娘，都很年轻，又都很寂寞，你的丈夫又是个很不难看的男人。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "夫人虽然是天香国色，但山珍海味吃久了，也想换换口味的……",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_lei_yu",
      "text": "不许你胡说！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你不信？要不要我带你去瞧瞧？那个小姑娘虽然没有你这么漂亮，却比你年轻，女人只要年轻，男人就有胃口。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我劝你，什么事还是看开些好，这里的人，本就对这种事看得很淡，就好像吃白饭一样，他能找别的女人，你为什么不能找别的男人？反正大家都是在找乐子，两人扯平，心里就会舒服些。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "来，用不着害臊，反正迟早总有一天，你也免不了要跟别人上……",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你这是敬酒不吃吃罚酒，到了这里，你就算真的三贞九烈，也不由得你不依，你逃也逃不了的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_lei_yu",
      "text": "站住，你再往前走一步，我金针就要你的命！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "金针？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_lei_yu",
      "text": "你既然也在江湖中走动过，总该听说过沈家的金针，见血封喉，百发百中，你有把握能避得开？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雷雨",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你是沈太君的什么人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_lei_yu",
      "text": "我就是她孙女……",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_su_yan",
      "text": "你笑什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_yan",
      "speaker_name": "苏燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我在笑你。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_su_yan",
      "text": "笑我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_yan",
      "speaker_name": "苏燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你呀，有了那么样一个漂亮的太太，还不老实。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_su_yan",
      "text": "有哪个男人是老实的？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_yan",
      "speaker_name": "苏燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "有人说，男人就像是茶壶，女人是茶杯，一个茶壶，总得配好几个茶杯。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_su_yan",
      "text": "比喻得妙极了，你这是听谁说的？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_yan",
      "speaker_name": "苏燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "自然是男人说的，可是……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_yan",
      "speaker_name": "苏燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "这里的女孩子个个都很漂亮，你为什么会挑上我？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_su_yan",
      "text": "一个人若要偷嘴吃，当然要挑最好吃的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_yan",
      "speaker_name": "苏燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "可是我连瞧都没有瞧过你一眼，你怎么知道我会上你的钩？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_su_yan",
      "text": "越是假正经的女人，越容易上钩，这道理男人都很明白。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_yan",
      "speaker_name": "苏燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "什么，你说我假正经？你以为我随随便便就会跟人家上床？老实告诉你，雷雨想勾我，已想得发疯，可是我瞧见他那一脸大麻子就生气。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 566
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_su_yan",
      "text": "麻子又有什么不好？十个麻子九个俏，有的女人还特别喜欢麻子哩！何况，熄了灯，还不都是一样。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 571
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_yan",
      "speaker_name": "苏燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我本来以为雷大麻子已经够坏的了，谁知道你比他更不是东西。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_su_yan",
      "text": "这里的男人除了龙飞骥外，大概没有一个好东西。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_yan",
      "speaker_name": "苏燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "一点也不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_su_yan",
      "text": "那两个老头子呢？除了下棋外，大概已没有什么别的兴趣了吧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 582
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_yan",
      "speaker_name": "苏燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "那你就错了，这两个老不死，人老心却不老，除了庄主留下来的之外，这里的女孩子哪个没有被他们欺负过？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 586
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_su_yan",
      "text": "雷雨的老婆呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 588,
      "line_end": 588
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_yan",
      "speaker_name": "苏燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "那两个骚狐狸，本就是自己送上门去的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 590,
      "line_end": 590
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_su_yan",
      "text": "雷雨难道甘心戴绿帽子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 592,
      "line_end": 592
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_yan",
      "speaker_name": "苏燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "雷大麻子在别人面前虽然耀武扬威，但见了他们两人，简直连屁都不敢放一个。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 594,
      "line_end": 596
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_su_yan",
      "text": "雷雨年轻力壮，又会武功，为什么要怕那两个糟老头子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 598,
      "line_end": 600
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_su_yan",
      "text": "这两个老头子武功难道比雷雨还高？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 604
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_su_yan",
      "text": "你可知道他们姓什么？叫什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 608,
      "line_end": 608
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_yan",
      "speaker_name": "苏燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 610,
      "line_end": 610
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_su_yan",
      "text": "他们是什么时候来的？这你总该知道了吧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 612,
      "line_end": 614
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_yan",
      "speaker_name": "苏燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "也不知道，我来的时候，他们已经在这里了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 616,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_su_yan",
      "text": "你是什么时候来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 618,
      "line_end": 618
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_yan",
      "speaker_name": "苏燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "有好几年了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 620,
      "line_end": 620
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_su_yan",
      "text": "你怎么会到这里来的呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 622,
      "line_end": 622
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_yan",
      "speaker_name": "苏燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "还不是跟你们一样，糊里糊涂的就来了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 624,
      "line_end": 624
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_su_yan",
      "text": "你年纪还轻，难道真要在这种鬼地方过一辈子？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 626,
      "line_end": 626
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_yan",
      "speaker_name": "苏燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "既已到了这里，还不是只有认命了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 628
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_yan",
      "speaker_name": "苏燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "大家开开心心的，为什么要谈这种事呢？来……",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 630,
      "line_end": 632
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_yan",
      "speaker_name": "苏燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你干什么？抽了筋？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 636
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_su_yan",
      "text": "不……不是，是我的伤……伤还没有好。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 638,
      "line_end": 638
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_yan",
      "speaker_name": "苏燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "挑来挑去，想不到却挑了你这个短命的病鬼！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 640,
      "line_end": 642
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你在外面吃过饭了？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 652,
      "line_end": 652
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "没有，你呢？……你为什么不先吃？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 654,
      "line_end": 654
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我……我还不饿。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 656,
      "line_end": 656
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "菜都凉了，你随便吃点吧……这些菜，本来都是你爱吃的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 658,
      "line_end": 660
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "这几天我已将这院子前前后后都量过了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 670,
      "line_end": 670
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 672,
      "line_end": 672
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我总觉得这地方绝不止二十八间屋子，本该至少有三十间的，只可惜我找来找去，也找不到多出来的那两间屋子在哪里？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 674,
      "line_end": 676
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "这里的女孩子很多，女孩子的嘴总比较快些，你为什么不去问问她们呢？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 678,
      "line_end": 680
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我本来是想问的，只可惜什么也没有问出来。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 690,
      "line_end": 690
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "但她们的口风越紧，越可证明她们必定有所隐瞒，证明这里必定有什么不可告人的秘密，我只要知道这点，也就够了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 692,
      "line_end": 694
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你不准备再去问她们了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 696,
      "line_end": 696
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "绝不会再去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 698,
      "line_end": 698
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "小姑娘已问过，明天我就该去问老头子了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 704,
      "line_end": 704
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我想……明天你一定会比今天回来得早。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 708,
      "line_end": 708
    }
